Type : Creational 
Puropse: Ensure a class allows only one object to be created, 
	providing a single point of access to it
Methods: 
	'Traditional' 
		--> make the constructor private
		--> provide public static getter returning a static instance of the Singleton
		--> using Syncrhonized and instance variable
	Enumeration
		--> Have one constant named "INSTANCE" -> representing the Singleton
		--> using Synchronized and instance variable
		--> !need to provide the public static getter returning the static instance of the Singleton
			--> NO CONSTRUCTOR NEEDED
		